approve(address,uint256).details: This function assumes the operator is attempting to approve      an ERC-721 if valueOrId_ is a possibly valid ERC-721 token id.      Unlike setApprovalForAll, spender_ must be allowed to be 0x0 so      that approval can be revoked.

erc20Approve(address,uint256).details: Providing type(uint256).max for approval value results in an      unlimited approval that is not deducted from on transfers.

erc20TransferFrom(address,address,uint25.details: 推荐使用此函数进行ERC20转账

erc721TransferFrom(address,address,uint2.details: 推荐使用此函数进行ERC721转账

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

permit(address,address,uint256,uint256,u.details: 如果permit的value值设为type(uint256).max，将产生一个无限制的授权额度，      在转账时不会从该额度中扣除

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

supportsInterface(bytes4).details: Returns true if this contract implements the interface defined by `interfaceId`. See the corresponding https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-165#how-interfaces-are-identified[ERC section] to learn more about how these ids are created. This function call must use less than 30 000 gas.

transfer(address,uint256).details: This function assumes the operator is attempting to transfer as ERC-20      given this function is only supported on the ERC-20 interface.      Treats even large amounts that are valid ERC-721 ids as ERC-20s.

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).details: 如果valueOrId是有效的代币ID，则该函数假定操作者试图转移ERC-721代币

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

DOMAIN_SEPARATOR().notice: Returns domain initial domain separator, or recomputes if chain id is not equal to initial chain id

depositTokens(uint256,address,uint256).notice: 向指定的 NFT 注入 ERC20 代币

depositTokens(uint256,uint256).notice: 向指定的NFT存入本合约的ERC20代币

erc721TransferExempt(address).notice: Function to check if address is transfer exempt

getTokenDeposits(uint256).notice: 获取指定 NFT 的所有存款信息

ownerOf(uint256).notice: Function to find owner of a given ERC-721 token

safeTransferFrom(address,address,uint256.notice: Function for ERC-721 transfers with contract support. This function only supports moving valid ERC-721 ids, as it does not exist on the ERC-20 spec and will revert otherwise.
Function for ERC-721 transfers with contract support and callback data. This function only supports moving valid ERC-721 ids, as it does not exist on the ERC-20 spec and will revert otherwise.

tokenURI(uint256).notice: tokenURI must be implemented by child contract

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).notice: 用于混合转账的函数，操作者可能与from地址不同

withdrawTokens(uint256,uint256).notice: 从指定的 NFT 中提取 ERC20 代币
